                            <comment id="15006892" author="ancosen" created="Mon, 16 Nov 2015 16:38:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Now it should be ok. I&apos;ve attached a five minutes Junit Producer Test with 500 messages. It looks good.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
